		 alpha?	( mirror://gentoo/ghc-bin-${PV}-alpha.tbz2 )
		 amd64?	( mirror://gentoo/ghc-bin-${PV}-amd64.tbz2 )
		 ppc?	( mirror://gentoo/ghc-bin-${PV}-ppc.tbz2 )
		 sparc?	( mirror://gentoo/ghc-bin-${PV}-sparc.tbz2 )
		 x86?	( mirror://gentoo/ghc-bin-${PV}-x86.tbz2 )"

